uk.co.strangeskies.fx

Interface TreeItemData<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the data
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TreeItemImpl.TreeItemDataImpl

    public interface TreeItemData<T>
    This interface defines the type of a TreeItem for a ModularTreeView. It provides access to the actual typed data of each node, as well as to the contributions which apply to that node, and the item data of the parent.
